  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为工业物联网系统画一个数据处理流程图。核心是从MQTT Broker收集遥测数据，然后经过分类、分析，最后生成可视化站点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那数据流入的入口是MQTT Broker推送到某个收件箱吗？还是直接处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "Inbox"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，MQTT Broker通过push操作把遥测流送到Inbox。这个Inbox我们叫TelemetryStream，是原始数据的缓冲池。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，已添加MQTT Broker到TelemetryStream的push流向。接下来怎么处理这些原始数据？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "Classified"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "TelemetryStream需要经过一个分类脚本classify-inbox.mjs处理，输出到Classified节点。注意这里Classified实际上还是MQTT Broker，但代表的是已分类的数据通道。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "Classified",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "有点困惑——Classified和MQTT Broker是同一个实体吗？还是复用标签？",
